<!-- Primary market: SA -->
<section class="section section--warm" aria-labelledby="market-title">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">Primary market</span>
      <h2 class="section-title" id="market-title">South Africa - AfricanSTN's operational base</h2>
      <div class="section-divider"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-visual reveal">
      <div>
        <p style="font-size:15px;color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:16px;">South Africa is the most developed sports technology market on the African continent. It combines strong commercial sports infrastructure, an active technology startup ecosystem, and a relatively advanced data protection environment, including POPIA.</p>
        <p style="font-size:15px;color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:16px;">For international companies entering Africa, South Africa provides a practical starting point - both as a market in its own right and as a gateway to broader continental expansion.</p>
        <p style="font-size:15px;color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.8;">AfricanSTN is based in South Africa and operates within the POPIA regulatory framework, using this as a foundation for engagement with both local and international stakeholders, while maintaining a continental perspective as the platform grows.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;">
        <div class="card card--gold-top" style="padding:20px;">
          <h3 style="font-size:15px;">Commercial sport</h3>
          <p>Strong professional leagues across football, rugby, and cricket, with established commercial structures and growing demand for technology.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card card--gold-top" style="padding:20px;">
          <h3 style="font-size:15px;">Technology sector</h3>
          <p>An active startup ecosystem, established tech infrastructure, and increasing investment in sports-adjacent technology.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card card--gold-top" style="padding:20px;">
          <h3 style="font-size:15px;">Regulatory maturity</h3>
          <p>POPIA provides a sophisticated data protection framework aligned with global standards, supporting compliance and creating confidence for international companies operating in the market.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

